charges.charge_disposition: Defendant Brown sentenced to suspended imposition of jgm and sen; dft placed on 3 years unsupervised probation on following terms and conditions: 1) do not drive w/any measurable amt of alcohol in system; 2) submit to testing as required by law enforcement officer; 3) pay fine of $440 and $10 s/a; 4) w/i 60 days as directed by probation, serve 2 consecutive days of confinement-may be served in community treatment center or similar facility; 5) dft to apy $45 month beg 11/5/92 and $45 month on 5th of each month thereafter (1-2)
